91932","overlay_opacity":40,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":60,"padding_top_m":0,"padding_bottom_m":36,"header_body_spacing":14,"header_body_spacing_m":16,"heading_font_size":48,"heading_font_size_m":37,"heading_max_width":540,"heading_max_width_m":320,"body_max_width":500,"body_max_width_m":320,"body_font_size_m":16}},"collection_rich_article_J3a3gw":{"type":"collection-rich-article","blocks":{"heading_gn34aG":{"type":"heading","settings":{"level":"h2","text":"About BEDGEAR Beauty","align":"center"}},"image_Ark9JE":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify://shop_images/07-Beauty-Pillow-Lifestyle2.jpg","alt":"","width":100,"float":"center","caption":"","align":"left"}},"text_8YQByV":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<p>At BEDGEAR, we believe better sleep fuels better performance — in life, in health, and even in how you feel and look every day. Our <em>Beauty Collection</em> is designed to enhance your skin’s natural recovery overnight, with fabrics that stay cool, dry, and clean. Each pillow, sheet, and protector is engineered to help your skin rest — so you wake up refreshed, rejuvenated, and ready to shine.</p>","align":"left"}},"quote_k7Vwkw":{"type":"quote","settings":{"quote":"<p><strong>“Sleep is not just rest — it’s recovery. Our mission is to engineer performance bedding that helps you look and feel your best, night after night.”</strong></p>","cite":"Eugene Alletto, CEO & Founder, BEDGEAR","align":"left"}},"heading_HJFfEM":{"type":"heading","settings":{"level":"h4","text":"What Is “Beauty Sleep” — and Is It Real?","align":"left"}},"text_URebt9":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<p>Yes — and science backs it up. Studies show that quality sleep promotes collagen production, balanced hydration, and cell repair — all crucial for maintaining healthy, glowing skin. During deep sleep, your body increases blood flow to the skin and reduces cortisol levels, which can help prevent breakouts and puffiness.</p>","align":"left"}},"text_ynikHM":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<p>At BEDGEAR, we’ve engineered bedding that complements your body’s natural nighttime recovery. Our <a href=\"https://bedgear.com/products/ver-tex-sheet-set\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bedgear.com/products/ver-tex-sheet-set\"><em>Ver-Tex™</em></a> and <a href=\"https://bedgear.com/products/dri-tec-sheet-set\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bedgear.com/products/dri-tec-sheet-set\"><em>Dri-Tec®</em></a> fabrics help regulate temperature and wick away moisture — reducing skin irritation and allowing your body to do what it does best: restore itself.</p>","align":"left"}},"quote_e6kCcX":{"type":"quote","settings":{"quote":"<p><strong>“Heat and humidity increase sebum production and inflammation, both of which can exacerbate acne.”</strong></p>","cite":"Dermatology Journal of Sleep and Skin Health, 2021","align":"left"}},"heading_piVCpV":{"type":"heading","settings":{"level":"h4","text":"The Best Pillow for Skin Health","align":"left"}},"text_aetnwL":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<p>Unlike traditional pillows that create friction, pressure, and heat buildup, the <a href=\"https://bedgear.com/products/beauty-performance-pillow\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bedgear.com/products/beauty-performance-pillow\">Beauty Performance® Pillow</a> is engineered to protect and promote healthier skin while you sleep.</p>","align":"left"}},"text_AjxQNB":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<p><strong>Ergonomic Shape for Reduced Pressure</strong></p><p>Its unique ergonomic shape gently cradles your face to minimize facial contact and pressure on delicate skin and lashes.</p>","align":"left"}},"text_DFp7P9":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li>Reduces sleep lines and creasing</li><li>Minimizes morning puffiness and inflammation</li><li>Eases stress on lashes to prevent breakage</li><li>Supports natural head and neck alignment</li></ul>","align":"left"}},"text_tVrh7V":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<p><strong>Top Picks:</strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://bedgear.com/products/balance-performance-pillow\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bedgear.com/products/balance-performance-pillow\"><strong>Balance Performance® Pillow</strong></a> – for combination sleepers seeking adaptive support.<br/></li><li><a href=\"https://bedgear.com/products/storm-performance-pillow\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bedgear.com/products/storm-performance-pillow\"><strong>Storm Performance® Pillow</strong></a> – for hot sleepers who want cooling comfort.<br/></li><li><a href=\"https://bedgear.com/products/beauty-performance-pillow\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bedgear.com/products/beauty-performance-pillow\"><strong>Beauty Performance® Pillow</strong> </a>– for beauty-focused sleepers who want smoother skin and cooling comfort.</li></ul>","align":"left"}},"image_pWiPdM":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify://shop_images/Beauty-Pillwo-Lifestyle-Model-06.jpg","alt":"","width":100,"float":"center","caption":"","align":"left"}},"heading_eHMFVY":{"type":"heading","settings":{"level":"h4","text":"Friction-Free Hyper-Silk®","align":"left"}},"text_kKFVWz":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<p>The luxuriously smooth, breathable Hyper-Silk® fabric eliminates friction to prevent damage to skin and lashes.</p>","align":"left"}},"text_GFgAhF":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li>Protects skin from irritation and inflammation</li><li>Prevents friction that contributes to sleep lines</li><li>Feels cool and luxurious against skin</li></ul>","align":"left"}},"heading_Tpe4fW":{"type":"heading","settings":{"level":"h4","text":"Enhanced Breathability","align":"left"}},"text_gVitf9":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<p>Air-X® Mesh and air vents promote continuous airflow to keep your skin cool and balanced.</p>","align":"left"}},"text_PkNyw9":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li>Reduces heat-related puffiness and inflammation</li><li>Helps prevent breakouts caused by excess heat and moisture</li><li>Keeps skin calm and less reactive</li><li>Promotes cooler, deeper sleep</li></ul>","align":"left"}},"heading_kC8zdw":{"type":"heading","settings":{"level":"h4","text":"Expert Tips for a Better Beauty Sleep Routine","align":"left"}},"text_RCqfXy":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<ol><li><strong>Wash pillowcases every 3–4 days.</strong><br/></li><li><strong>Keep your bedroom below 70°F.</strong><br/></li><li><strong>Avoid alcohol or sugar before bed.</strong><br/></li><li><strong>Use a pillow that fits your sleep position and temperature profile.</strong><br/></li></ol><p></p>","align":"left"}},"quote_X4VDrL":{"type":"quote","settings":{"quote":"<p><em><strong>“Investing in the right bedding isn’t a luxury — it’s an extension of your skincare routine.”</strong></em></p>","cite":"Eugene Alletto, CEO & Founder, BEDGEAR","align":"left"}},"text_HXGVpH":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<p><strong>Also Read:</strong></p>","align":"left"}},"text_j7QwBP":{"type":"text","settings":{"content":"<p><a href=\"https://bedgear.com/blogs/news/the-secret-to-waking-up-beautiful-it-s-not-what-you-think\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bedgear.com/blogs/news/the-secret-to-waking-up-beautiful-it-s-not-what-you-think\">The Secret to Waking Up Beautiful (It’s Not What You Think)</a></p><p><a href=\"https://bedgear.com/blogs/news/discover-the-perfect-performance-sheets-for-every-season-with-bedgear\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bedgear.com/blogs/news/discover-the-perfect-performance-sheets-for-every-season-with-bedgear\">Discover the Perfect Performance® Sheets for Every Season with BEDGEAR</a></p><p><a href=\"https://bedgear.com/blogs/news/why-great-sleep-goes-beyond-the-mattress-the-essential-role-of-pillows-sheets-and-protectors\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://bedgear.com/blogs/news/why-great-sleep-goes-beyond-the-mattress-the-essential-role-of-pillows-sheets-and-protectors\">Why Great Sleep Goes Beyond the Mattress: The Essential Role of Pillows, Sheets, and Protectors</a></p>","align":"left"}},"faq_KVaqFA":{"type":"faq","settings":{"question":"Do pillows really affect my skin?","answer":"<p>Absolutely. Dirty or heat-trapping pillows can harbor bacteria and oil, which can worsen acne and irritation. Cooling, moisture-wicking fabrics help your skin stay clean and balanced overnight.</p>","open_by_default":false}},"faq_PCHmVH":{"type":"faq","settings":{"question":"How often should I replace my pillow?","answer":"<p>Every 18–24 months for optimal hygiene and support. Performance pillows like BEDGEAR’s can last longer due to removable, washable covers and antimicrobial fabrics.</p>","open_by_default":false}},"faq_GimwAN":{"type":"faq","settings":{"question":"Can bedding really help with wrinkles?","answer":"<p>Yes. Reducing heat, friction, and pressure points can help prevent premature sleep lines. Ergonomic support also reduces facial compression overnight.</p>","open_by_default":false}},"callout_imGeRB":{"type":"callout","settings":{"variant":"info","bordered":false,"accent_bar":true,"title":"Sources:","content":"<p><em>1. Journal of Clinical Sleep Medicine</em> (2021). <em>“Physiological Skin Recovery During Sleep.”<br/>2. Dermatology and Therapy Review</em> (2020). <em>“Environmental Influence on Sebum and Acne Formation.”<br/>3. Textile Research Journal</em> (2022). <em>“Fabric Properties and Their Effect on Skin Microclimate.”<br/>4. Sleep Foundation</em> (2023). <em>“How Sleep Affects Skin Health and Collagen Production.”</em></p>","align":"left"}}},"block_order":["heading_gn34aG","image_Ark9JE","text_8YQByV","quote_k7Vwkw","heading_HJFfEM","text_URebt9","text_ynikHM","quote_e6kCcX","heading_piVCpV","text_aetnwL","text_AjxQNB","text_DFp7P9","text_tVrh7V","image_pWiPdM","heading_eHMFVY","text_kKFVWz","text_GFgAhF","heading_Tpe4fW","text_gVitf9","text_PkNyw9","heading_kC8zdw","text_RCqfXy","quote_X4VDrL","text_